name: Professional Logo Manipulation
description: Logo design & professional branding for your company and/or service(s). Logo Manipulation is simply an excellent, quick service whereby using the internet, conference telephone calls and video-chat you can speak to one of our professional designers about what you want the logo for your company to be based around, along with suggestions of your own until you're happy with the final product. We are excellent communicators and have years of experience in the design industry and encourage our clients to be involved in every step of the design process so that every customer has the same enjoyable experience that ends with exactly what they want: a great design.

name: Business Card Creation
description:
Our team of designers will keep in touch with you and using your (already made) logo will create an interesting and inspiring business card that's sure to grab someone's attention and tailor it to your exact specifications.
Images are raster based at 300PPI and include CMYK colouring.

name: Anything & Everything
description: This package is simply anything you want it to be, if you're wanting anything from the below list, or even anything not on the list, then feel free to use the contact form to the bottom-right of the page for work on anything else. - Posters - Web-banners - Flyers - Letterheads - Advertisements - T-shirt designs - Band logos - P.O.S etc. This product is simply a deposit for any type of work to be undergone by our designers and is deducted from your final bill, but if you fail to contact us within 180 days of placing your deposit, you will lose it. Thanks for taking the time to view our website. If you have any concerns or questions, please use the "Contact us" form to your right.
